          <div class="col-lg-9" style="    padding: 35px;">
                <h5><b>Home Loan</b></h5>
                <p>Covered under Retail Banking</p>
                <h5><b>Purpose:</b></h5>
                <ul>
                    <li>Purchase of Residential property, Apartment, Row House or Bungalow</li>
                    <li>Home Loan for Construction </li>
                    <li>House Renovation Loan</li>
                    <li>Home Extension Loan</li>
                    <li>Balance Transfer </li>
                    <li>Home Loan Top-up</li>   
                </ul>
                
                <h5><b>Key Features:</b></h5>
                <ul>
                <li>Flexible loan amounts based on the property value and borrower's eligibility</li>
                <li>Competitive interest rates with options for fixed or variable rates</li>
                <li>Loan terms tailored to suit the borrower's financial situation, ranging from 10 to 30 years</li>
                <li>Option to choose between different repayment plans, including equal monthly instalments (EMI), customized repayment schedules</li>
                <li>High loan-to-value (LTV) ratio, allowing borrowers to finance up to a certain percentage (up to 80%) of the property's value</li>
